<A>__{jack returns to his post.}
<C>__{jack}
<D>__{continue due west, mr. bonden.}
<A>__{tom pullings watches him. there has been a change amongst the officers and crew toward jack. his relentless driving after the acheron has reached the point of obsession, an obsession not shared by his exhausted men. he is a lonely, haunted figure as he now steps up on the gunwale, one hand on the ratlines, scanning the empty sea, sensing his enemy is out there, just beyond the curve of the earth.}
